OL,3,CMen accused of taking part in violent
OL,4,Cdisorder in Hartlepool appear in court
OL,6,FThree man alleged to have taken part
OL,7,Fin violent disorder in Hartlepool on
OL,8,FWednesday night have been remanded in
OL,9,Fcustody.
OL,11,FAnthony Allen, 42, of Ormesby Road,
OL,12,FHartlepool, appeared at Teesside
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court, charged with
OL,14,Fviolent disorder and assaulting an
OL,15,Femergency worker.
OL,17,FJames Elliott, 41, of Raby Road,
OL,18,FHartlepool, was with him in the dock,
OL,19,Fcharged with violent disorder.
