OL,3,CMen accused of taking part in violent
OL,4,Cdisorder in Hartlepool appear in court
OL,6,FPeter Clark, 47, of no fixed address,
OL,7,Fappearing separately, was charged with
OL,8,Fviolent disorder and exposure after
OL,9,Fallegedly showing his buttocks and
OL,10,Fgenitalia to police.
OL,12,FNo pleas were entered to any of the
OL,13,Fcharges.
OL,15,FPaul Doney, prosecuting, told Teesside
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court that 200 people
OL,17,Fwere in a group which initially met at
OL,18,Fthe Cenotaph in Hartlepool on
OL,19,FWednesday evening, and they moved
OL,20,Ftowards mosques and a community centre.
